headline: IQVIA CFO Ron Bruehlman to speak at the Bank of America Annual Health Care Conference on May 13
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., May 07, 2025--IQVIA Holdings Inc. ("IQVIA") (NYSE:IQV) announced today that Ron Bruehlman, executive vice president and chief financial officer, will speak at the Bank of America Annual Health Care Conference on Tuesday, May 13, 2025, at 5:20 p.m. ET (2:20 p.m. local PT).
